19:49.760 --> 19:54.546
When Paul writes to the Ephesians, and he begins with that great poem of praise,

19:54.658 --> 19:57.662
of the amazing elect and grace of God.

19:59.244 --> 20:14.766
He's way up in the heights, and then you get to the 13th verse, and he says, and you also were included in Christ when you heard the word of truth, the gospel of your salvation.

20:16.148 --> 20:17.169
Are you in Christ?

20:20.334 --> 20:23.538
